metadata.name: Tropical Express
metadata.description: Vibrant colors from a beautiful day. Drone Images are made for days like this. Good friend professional bodyboarder Andre Botha is at the office. Paparazzi is on the job. Andre is from South Africa  youngest  World Champion at the age of 17.  Very unique perspective that features so much in one image. From the rainbow off the back and the intensity of the drop. Where the paparazzi is kneeling water depth 1-2ft tops.
